      "id": "PopularPost46033",
      "post_content": "Conversion is a mean card. Denying your opponent access to red mana by turning his Mountains into Plains is just cruel. Use Magical Hack in combination with Conversion to hose ANY color except for white. Once the combo is in place, if your opponent doesn't have [Birds of Paradise](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Birds of Paradise) or (LOL) [Celestial Prism](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Celestial Prism), its unlikely he'll be able to cast any spell to get rid of it. Pure red mages have been known to sideboard a playset of [Disenchant](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Disenchant)s into their deck to deal with Conversions - or alternately, play [Sunglasses of Urza](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sunglasses of Urza). Players who played both red and white sometimes played Conversion AND Sunglasses of Urza to turn all of their lands into [Plateau](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Plateau)s. The upkeep of Conversion made this a bit unwieldy. ",
      "posted_by": "Eppek_the_Goblin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost46033\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Conversion is a mean card.  Denying your opponent access to red mana by turning his Mountains into Plains is just cruel.  Use Magical Hack in combination with Conversion to hose ANY color except for white.  Once the combo is in place, if your opponent doesn't have <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Birds of Paradise\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Birds of Paradise\">Birds of Paradise</a> or (LOL) <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Celestial Prism\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Celestial Prism\">Celestial Prism</a>, its unlikely he'll be able to cast any spell to get rid of it.  Pure red mages have been known to sideboard a playset of <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Disenchant\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Disenchant\">Disenchant</a>s into their deck to deal with Conversions - or alternately, play <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sunglasses of Urza\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sunglasses of Urza\">Sunglasses of Urza</a>.  Players who played both red and white sometimes played Conversion AND Sunglasses of Urza to turn all of their lands into <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Plateau\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Plateau\">Plateau</a>s.  The upkeep of Conversion made this a bit unwieldy. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '46033'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy525\">Eppek_the_Goblin</span>\r\n                                (1/14/2010 9:56:57 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
